        <buy_head>How to Buy and How to use ?</buy_head>
        <buydescription>
            <line1> <![CDATA[ Gift cards are available for purchase on our website and in our physical stores. you can also Call 218957982 to purchase gift cards and experience gift cards over the phone ]]> </line1>
            <line2> <![CDATA[On the website, shop as usual, then proceed to the checkout. You'll be prompted to input two codes for each voucher you want to use at checkout.]]></line2>
            <line3> <![CDATA[ the 10-digit serial number on the bottom right of the voucher]]></line3>
            <line4> <![CDATA[ the 7-character online security code underneath the scratch-off panel on back of the card]]></line4>
            <line5> <![CDATA[ for multiple gift vouchers, enter one set of voucher codes at a time]]></line5>
             <line6> <![CDATA[ After entering in the gift voucher codes, your order will be automatically updated with credit to the value of the voucher(s). If there's any balance to pay, you can use a debit or credit card in the usual way.Gift vouchers have no expiry date; please note this is different to our gift cards which expire after 2 years.Gift vouchers can only be used once, and they cannot be used in our shops once the holographic panel has been scratched off. ]]> </line6>
        </buydescription>
    </buy_Giftcards>

